# Site Independence Rule

- Never add runtime imports from `Main Runner - Career Path` to `Main Runner - Lineups` or vice versa.
- If a shared improvement applies to both sites, implement the same change in both folders.
- If one site-specific feature is added, keep it self-contained in that site folder.
- Assume either folder may be deleted; the remaining site must still run unchanged.
